00249     template <typename N>
00250             Vector<3, N> vcross (Vector<3, N> a, Vector<3, N> b) {
00251         static Vector<3, N> c;
00252 
00253         c[0] = a[1]*b[2]-a[2]*b[1];
00254         c[1] = a[2]*b[0]-a[0]*b[2];
00255         c[2] = a[0]*b[1]-a[1]*b[0];
00256 
00257         return c;
00258     }

00265     template <typename N>
00266             Vector<4, N> vcross (Vector<4, N> a, Vector<4, N> b, Vector<4, N> c) {
00267         static Vector<4, N> d;
00268         N A = b[0]*c[1]-b[1]*c[0],
00269         B = b[0]*c[2]-b[2]*c[0],
00270         C = b[0]*c[3]-b[3]*c[0],
00271         D = b[1]*c[2]-b[2]*c[1],
00272         E = b[1]*c[3]-b[3]*c[1],
00273         F = b[2]*c[3]-b[3]*c[2];
00274 
00275         d[0] =  a[1]*F - a[2]*E + a[3]*D;
00276         d[1] = -a[0]*F + a[2]*C - a[3]*B;
00277         d[2] =  a[0]*E - a[1]*C + a[3]*A;
00278         d[3] = -a[0]*D + a[1]*B - a[2]*A;
00279 
00280         return d;
00281     }

00286     template <unsigned D, typename N>
00287             Vector<D, N> vnormalize( const Vector<D, N> &x ) {
00288         static Vector<D, N> n;
00289         N norm = sqrt ( x.sqnorm() );
00290         for ( unsigned i = 0; i < D; i++ ) n[i] = x[i]/norm;
00291         return n;
